summary: Changes the appearance of some of the game\'s important characters.
descriptionHtml:
Changes the appearance of some of the game\'s important characters.
Includes:
    Wood Elf Cicero, Nord Karliah, Redguard Delvin, and more.
It also adds a new Companions member named Ra\'Gru Ogar, an orc follower.
 I know this mod isn\'t very impressive, but I\'m very new at modding, this was basically for practice and for anyone who would want it by some chance.
author: Zacharyyyyyyy
